edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.common
Class FieldNames

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--edu.columbia.cs.sdarts.common.FieldNames
public class FieldNames
extends java.lang.Object

A "constants container" for all legal STARTS field names and codes. Whenever referring to STARTS fields by name or code, always use these constants. This minimizes the impact of change, should a field name ever change.
